er Begriff der ‚Jüdischen Kunst’ untersucht.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mai 2021) 7aART / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Ebook Package 2020z978311069627108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Arts 2020z9783110704655oZDB-23-DPK08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020z9783110704518oZDB-23-DGG0 cprintz978311061506740uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311069398040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110693980423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110693980.jpg  a978-3-11-069627-1  DG Ebook Package 2020b2020  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_CL_MUAR  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2020  aZDB-23-DPKb2020